name: Tettei Kaiseki: Hisshou Pachi-Slot Doujou: Yamasa & Pioneer
overview: Tettei Kaiseki - Hissyou Pachislot Doujyho - Yamasa & Pioneer is a pachinko slot machine simulator that features 5 pachinko slot machines (Deru Deru Kozou, Wai 2 Pulsar, Son'na Kaba Na!!, Bun Bun Bun & Vegetan V) made by Yamasa & Pioneer with all the machines stats avaliables.
